# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

### Changed
- Plan for more checks on type hints.
- Future refactor.


## [1.0.4] - 2020-11-04

### Changed
- Added requests to install_requires.


## [1.0.3] - 2020-11-04

### Changed
- Pylint review and check exceptions to improve quality.
- Minor changes on typos and other texts.
- Review of type hints to make the code more homogeneous.


## [1.0.2] - 2020-07-14

### Changed
- Replaced package paths: blueliv.api. -> blueliv


## [1.0.1] - 2020-07-13

### Added
- license='MIT' to the setup.py. Adding details on Classifiers is not enough.
- license_file = LICENSE in setup.cfp (metadata). Not required, but...
- created this CHANGELOG file.

### Changed
- Rename the 'api' directory to 'blueliv'


## [1.0.0] - 2020-06-12
- Initial package version